('9799fb41-aed1-4bb6-94e1-854d909a3666', 'msg_tutor', 'send_message', '{"text":"\uD83C\uDF93 *Find Your Perfect Tutor*\n\nBrowse *verified, rated teachers* for every subject \u2014 online or in-person.\n\n\u2B50 Read reviews \u00b7 Compare profiles \u00b7 Book instantly\n\n\uD83D\uDC49 Start here:\nhttps://www.suganta.com/teachers\n\n*Tip:* Create a free account to save favourites & get matched faster!","next_node_key":"post_action"}'::jsonb, 0, 0),
